import HomepageTemplate from '../components/Homepage.js';
export default HomepageTemplate;

<Tabs>
<Tab label="IBM CLOUD">
## What we offer?
- Includes dedicated infrastructure in an IBM data center with single availability zone deployment, software, and services.
- Set monthly charge with no user restrictions or hidden fees for exceeding capacity.
- Additional nodes can be added.
- Bare Metal availability.
- Bring your own license model (does not include licensing).
- Duration minimums apply.
- 24/7 support & monitoring patches & upgrades.
- Single point of contact solution level availability scalable.
</Tab>
<Tab label="Amazon Web Services">
## What we offer?
- Includes dedicated infrastructure in an AWS data center with single availability zone deployment, software, and services.
- Set monthly charge with no user restrictions or hidden fees for exceeding capacity.
- Additional nodes can be added to scale at $3k USD per month.
- Bring your own license model (does not include licensing).
- Duration minimums apply.
- 24/7 support & monitoring patches & upgrades.
- Single point of contact solution level availability scalable.
</Tab>
<Tab label="Microsoft Azure">

</Tab>

</Tab>
